<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>CEUNAK LUHTER TUAH CH267</title>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Na pumsa sualnak nih khan an tei dengmang, Vawlei cung tukforhnak kha
 phan awk a si, Khuamui chuahter law, ceunak lam kha hung tuah, Ceunak kha
 hung lut ko seh.

[C1]
   Ceunak kha luhter ko tuah, Ceunak kha luhter ko tuah, Na lung chung
   innkhar vialte kha hung hna law, Ceunak kha hung lut ko seh.

[V2]
 Pathian na zumhnak kha a rawh dengmang i, Na halnak vialte zong kha na
 sungh hmanh ah, Na lung chung innkhar vialte kha hung hna law, Ceunak kha
 luhter ko tuah.

[C2]
   Ceunak kha luhter ko tuah, Ceunak kha luhter ko tuah, Na lung chung
   innkhar vialte kha hung hna law, Ceunak kha hung lut ko seh.

[V3]
 Lunglawmhnak in ceunak kha rak tlai ko cang, Nangmah an thiantertu kha
 a si ngaingai, Sual muihnak thianter law, a lam kha awnh tuah, Ceunak a
 hung lut zau lai.

[C3]
   Ceunak kha luhter ko tuah, Ceunak kha luhter ko tuah, Na lung chung
   innkhar vialte kha hung hna law, Ceunak kha hung lut ko seh.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>267</hymn_number>
</song>